{
  "id": "adv_bond_ski_01_04",
  "title": "白石沙季4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、やっぱり私のトークに足りないものは……\n間違いないわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ so what my talk was missing was…\nThere's no doubt about it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ！？\nえっ、ど、ど、どうしたの、お姉ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha-!?\nWh-wh-what's wrong‚ Big Sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.599999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "聞いて、千紗。お姉ちゃん分かったの！\n私のトークには、オチが足りなかったんだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ Chisa. I've finally figured it out!\nMy talks were missing a \"Punch-Line\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5666656811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんだ……？　えっと……\n言われてみれば、『話のオチ』って言葉、よく聞くかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ is that it…? Um…\nCome to think of it‚ I do hear the term \"Punch-Line\" a lot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4333323478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、私の分析によると、話の大半はオチで決まるの\n最初の掴み以上に、最後のインパクトが大事なのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. According to my analysis‚ most talks are decided by the \"Punch-Line\"\nThe final impact is more important than the initial hook",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5666656811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "それを踏まえて\n今から滑らない話をするから、聞いてもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Keeping that in mind\nI'm going to tell a story that's guaranteed to land. Can you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7999990145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "も、物凄くハードルが上がってる気がするけど……\nうん、聞かせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like you're setting the bar incredibly high‚ but…\nSure‚ tell me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9333323478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "この前、寮であった話なんだけど、すずちゃんが\nポテトチップスを食べようとしたら、中身が空っぽで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this happened at the dorm the other day. Suzu-chan\ntried to eat some potato chips‚ but the bag was empty",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3999990145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "よく見たら、そばにいたこころちゃんの口元に\nポテトチップスの青のりがついててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking closely‚ on Kokoro-chan's face nearby\nwere some green seaweed flakes from the chips",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1666656811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "「また勝手に食べましたわね！」って、すずちゃんが\n怒ろうとしたら、すでにこころちゃんは逃げちゃってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan said‚ \"You ate them without asking again!\"\nand tried to get angry‚ but Kokoro-chan had already run away",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3666656811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんってば、リビングで一人\n「毎度毎度、こころはなんなんですのー！？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So there was Suzu-chan‚ all alone in the living room\nyelling‚ \"Every single time‚ what is wrong with Kokoro!?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5999990145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "「こころディスタンスですわー！」って\n怜ちゃんと芽衣ちゃんの曲名をもじって怒ってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"It's Kokoro Distance!!\"\ngetting angry by parodizing Rei and Mei's song title",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4666656811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それを怜ちゃんがたまたま聞いてて\n「何イジってるのよ！」って怒られちゃってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rei-chan happened to overhear that\nand Suzu-chan got scolded‚ \"What are you doing messing with our song title?!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1999990145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふっ、怒ってた方が怒られちゃったんだ\n面白いね。それがオチ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ so the one who was angry ended up being scolded instead\nThat's funny. So that's the \"Punch-Line\"——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3999990145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "っていうのは全部、夢だったんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "——…but that was all just a dream",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6999979972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "夢オチっっ！？\nえっと、それはオチの意味が違うような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A it-was-all-a-dream \"ending\"!?\nUm‚ I think that's a different kind of \"Punch-Line\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333313305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "そう？\nじゃあみんな、爆発しちゃうっていうのはどうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\nThen how about having everyone suddenly explode?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0666646639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "爆発オチも違うと思うよ……！？\nそれって、オチはオチでも、物語のオチだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think an explosion twist is also wrong…!\nThat's a twist‚ but it's more like a story's ending…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3333313305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして違った？　ちゃんと『話のオチ』って\n調べて、ノートにまとめたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was I wrong? I even researched it properly\nand took notes on \"Punch-Line\" and everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6333313305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "何が違うのかしら……うぅ、もっと研究しないと……！\nとりあえず、次は出オチっていうのを使って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what's different… Ugh‚ I need to study more…!\nFor now‚ next time I'll try using a \"first-sight gag\"…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9999979972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_04-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃん\nオチを考える前に、ひとまず落ち着いて～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-Big Sister\nBefore you think about \"Punch-Lines\"‚ just settle down for a bit~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2333353995,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}